<button id="modal-click" value="" style="display: none;" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalSelector"></button>

<div id="modalSelector" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
 <div class="modal-dialog">

  <!-- Modal content-->
  <div class="modal-content">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
      <h4 class="modal-title">Welcome to Medi-co:<br> A Quick Tour</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div id="doc-left" class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
        <p>1. Stay on top of your daily patients and to-dos with your profile's professional and convenient updates. </p>
        <%= image_tag('https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/medi-co/Icons/med_reminder.png', :width=>151, class: "text-center") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="doc-center" class="row hidden">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
        <p>2. Talk to your patients and send secure documents and updates, using Medi-Co's chat feature. </p>
        <%= image_tag('https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/medi-co/Icons/smart_phone.png', :width=>127, class: "text-center") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="doc-right" class="row hidden">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
        <p>3. Want to take your care further? Set up an appointment at your convenience, right from  your dashboard! </p>
        <%= image_tag('https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/medi-co/Icons/schedule_icon+2.png', :width=>154, class: "text-center") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <div class="onboard-modal-buttons btn-group" role="group"">
      <button type="button" id="btn-one" class="btn btn-primary">1</button>
      <button type="button" id="btn-two" class="btn btn-primary">2</button>
      <button type="button" id="btn-three" class="btn btn-primary">3</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
